  <entry>
    <title>OsStart</title>
    <url>/2022/01/29/OsStart/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="操作系统的启动">操作系统的启动<a title="#操作系统的启动" href="#操作系统的启动"></a></h1>
<h2 id="从图灵机到通用图灵机">从图灵机到通用图灵机<a title="#从图灵机到通用图灵机" href="#从图灵机到通用图灵机"></a></h2>
<p><img src="/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart.png" alt="Untitled" loading="lazy" class="φbp"></p>
<h2 id="从通用图灵机到计算机">从通用图灵机到计算机<a title="#从通用图灵机到计算机" href="#从通用图灵机到计算机"></a></h2>
<p><img src="/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart1.png" alt="Untitled" loading="lazy" class="φbp"></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="x86pc的开机过程">x86PC的开机过程<a title="#x86pc的开机过程" href="#x86pc的开机过程"></a></h2>
<ol>
<li>开机时，CS=0xFFFF; IP=0x0000（和保护模式对应，实模式的寻址CS:IP(CS左移4位+IP)，和保护模式不一样）</li>
<li>寻址0xFFFF0(ROM BIOS映射区)（0xFFFF0 = CS &lt;&lt; 4 + IP）</li>
<li>检查RAM，键盘，显示器，软硬磁盘（检查是否有硬件损坏）</li>
<li>将磁盘0磁道0扇区读入0x7c00处</li>
<li>设置CS=0x07c0, IP=0x0000</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart2.png" alt="Untitled" loading="lazy" class="φbp"></p>
<hr>
<aside>
💡 0x7c00处存放的代码就是从磁盘引导扇区读入的那512个字节
</aside>
<ul>
<li>引导扇区就是启动设备的第一个扇区</li>
<li>启动设备信息被设置在CMOS中</li>
<li>因此，磁盘的第一个扇区存放着开机后执行的第一段我们可以控制的程序</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="引导扇区代码：bootsect.s（汇编代码）">引导扇区代码：bootsect.s（汇编代码）<a title="#引导扇区代码：bootsect.s（汇编代码）" href="#引导扇区代码：bootsect.s（汇编代码）"></a></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>bootsect.s首先把自己从内存0x7c00的位置挪到0x90000的位置，为后续读入OS代码腾空间。然后从磁盘将setup程序（占4个扇区）读入内存0x90200，然后打印开机logo（如system is loading…，logo可修改，如下图），然后调用13号中断，继续读入system模块（OS代码）。bootsect.s的功能就结束了。bootsect.s的最后一行跳转到了setup所在的0x90200位置，开始执行setup程序</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart3.png" alt="Untitled" loading="lazy" class="φbp"></p>
<aside>
💡 BOOTSEG = 0x07c0
INITSEG = 0x9000
SETUPSEG = 0x9020
</aside>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.globl begtext,begdata,begbss,endtext,enddata,endbss</span><br><span class="line">.text  //文本段</span><br><span class="line">begtext:</span><br><span class="line">.data  //数据段</span><br><span class="line">begdata:</span><br><span class="line">.bss   //未初始化数据段</span><br><span class="line">begbss:</span><br><span class="line">entry start //关键字entry告诉链接器“程序入口”</span><br><span class="line">start:</span><br><span class="line">  mov ax, #BOOTSEG</span><br><span class="line">  mov ds, ax</span><br><span class="line">  mov ax, #INITSEG</span><br><span class="line">  mov es, ax </span><br><span class="line">  mov cx, #256</span><br><span class="line">  sub si, si</span><br><span class="line">  sub di, di</span><br><span class="line">  rep movw //到这里上面语句的作用就是将0x07c0:0x0000处的256个字（512字节）移动到0x9000:0x0000处</span><br><span class="line">  jmpi go, INITSEG //跳转到地址INITSEG:go处</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">go:</span><br><span class="line">  mov ax, cs //cs = 0x9000</span><br><span class="line">  mov ds, ax</span><br><span class="line">  mov es, ax</span><br><span class="line">  mov ss. ax</span><br><span class="line">  mov sp, #0xff00</span><br><span class="line">load_setup: //载入setup模块</span><br><span class="line">  mov dx, #0x0000</span><br><span class="line">  mov cx, #0x0002</span><br><span class="line">  mov bx, #0x0200</span><br><span class="line">  mov ax, #0x0200+SETUPLEN</span><br><span class="line">  int 0x13 //利用0x13中断将四个setup扇区读入，0x13的详细解释请见[https://wenku.baidu.com/view/71d73e460c22590103029d58.html?re=view](https://wenku.baidu.com/view/71d73e460c22590103029d58.html?re=view)</span><br><span class="line">  jnc ok_load_setup//如果0x13中断读取有错误会在CF位上置位，所以如果未置位就可以正常跳转到ok_load_setup函数处执行，所以这里要用jnc跳转</span><br><span class="line">  mov dx. #0x0000//如果上面的0x13中断执行错误，就复位驱动器再来一遍</span><br><span class="line">  mov ax, #0x0000</span><br><span class="line">  int 0x13</span><br><span class="line">  j   load_setup//又跳回到上面重新来循环</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/2022/01/28/OsStart/OsStart4.png" alt="Untitled" loading="lazy" class="φbp"></p>
<h3 id="读入setup模块后：执行ok_load_setup">读入setup模块后：执行ok_load_setup<a title="#读入setup模块后：执行ok_load_setup" href="#读入setup模块后：执行ok_load_setup"></a></h3>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Ok_load_setip: //载入setup模块</span><br><span class="line">  mov dl, #0x00</span><br><span class="line">  mov ax, #0x800 //ah=8获得磁盘参数</span><br><span class="line">  int 0x13</span><br><span class="line">  mov ch, #0x00</span><br><span class="line">  mov sectors, cx</span><br><span class="line">  mov ah, 0x03</span><br><span class="line">  xor bh, bh</span><br><span class="line">  [int 0x10](https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/INT_10H) //功能代码ah为0x03，所以这里0x10中断作用为读取光标位置</span><br><span class="line">  mov cx, #24</span><br><span class="line">  mov bx, #0x0007 //7是属性</span><br><span class="line">  mov bp, #msg1</span><br><span class="line">  mov ax, #1301</span><br><span class="line">  [int 0x10](https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/INT_10H) //功能代码ah为0x13，所以这里0x10中断作用为显示字符，即显示系统logo</span><br><span class="line">  mov ax, #SYSSEG //SYSSEG=0x1000</span><br><span class="line">  mov es, ax</span><br><span class="line">  call read_it //读入system模块</span><br><span class="line">  jmpi 0, SETUPSEG //转入0x9020:0x0000执行setup.s</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<aside>
💡 bootsect.s中的数据 //在文件末尾
<p>sectors:  .word  0</p>
<p>msgl: .byte  13 , 10</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">     .ascii “Loading system...”（开机语句，可修改）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.byte 13 , 10 , 13 , 10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</aside>
<h3 id="read_it-//读入system模块">read_it //读入system模块<a title="#read_it-//读入system模块" href="#read_it-//读入system模块"></a></h3>
<ul>
<li>system模块可能很大，要跨越磁道，所以还要定义一个函数来读入（也是用0x13中断来读）</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">read_it:</span><br><span class="line">  mov ax, es</span><br><span class="line">  cmp ax, #ENDSEG</span><br><span class="line">  jb ok1_read</span><br><span class="line">ok1_read:</span><br><span class="line">  mov ax, sectors</span><br><span class="line">  sub ax, sread //sread是当前磁道已读扇区数，ax未读扇区数</span><br><span class="line">  call read_track //读磁道</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>引导扇区的末尾 //BIOS用以识别引导扇区</li>
